<div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">

	<p n="1-2">
		Twenty-sixth year of the victorious king Kampavikramvarman.
	</p>

	<p n="4-9">
		The Caḻaiyāppāṟai field that Cayavallavaṉ, a merchant <supplied reason="subaudible">from</supplied> Kuḷattūr in the Teṉṉāṟṟūrnaṭu in the Palkuṉṟakōṭṭam, made as land for the tank, after buying it from the villagers of  Kuḷattūr, has been made as land for the tank.
	</p>

	<p n="9-12">
		The feet of he who ... to this are on my head.
	</p>


